    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Blazing orbs of fire plummet to the ground at four different points you can see within range. Each creature in a 40-foot-radius sphere centered on each point you choose must make a Dexterity saving throw. The sphere spreads around corners. A creature takes [[/damage 20d6 type=fire]] damage and [[/damage 20d6 type=bludgeoning]] damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature in the area of more than one fiery burst is affected only once.</p><p>The spell damages objects in the area and ignites flammable objects that aren't being worn or carried.</p></div>",
